有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 南博一2月21日，美国卫生官员表示，美国正在为新冠病毒社区传播的可能性做准备，若开始社区传播，企业和学校将被迫关闭。
NEW YORK (Reuters) - Health officials said the United States is preparing for the possibility of a new outbreak of the virus, forcing businesses and schools to close if community transmission begins.
据路透社22日报道，美国尚未出现新冠病毒的社区传播，但美国疾控中心官员南希·梅森尼尔（Nancy Messonnier）21日在电话记者会上指出，卫生部门正在为这种风险做准备。
But Nancy Messonnier, an official at the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention in the United States, said at a telephone news conference on Monday that the health authorities were preparing for the risk.
梅森尼尔表示，在未来几周内，如果新冠病毒开始在美国社区传播，卫生部门将会不得不采取类似亚洲国家采取的一些措施，做好学校停课、企业停工的准备。
In the next few weeks, if the virus starts to spread in the U.S. community, health authorities will have to take steps similar to those being taken in Asia to prepare schools to close and businesses to stop, Mason Neal said.
“我们尚未看到新冠病毒在美国进入社区传播的阶段，但这很有可能发生。
"We have not yet seen the new crown virus enter the community transmission stage in the United States, but it is very likely to happen.
”梅森尼尔称，“我们现在的目标仍然是减缓新冠病毒在美国的传播速度。
"Our goal is still to slow the spread of the new crown virus in the United States," Mason Neal said.
这会让我们赢得更多时间，为治疗更多病例和应对病毒持续传播做好准备。
That will buy us more time to prepare for more cases and for the continued spread of the virus.
”美国疾控中心称，目前在美国境内有13例新冠肺炎确诊病例。
The CDC says there are 13 confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia in the United States.
另外在从中国武汉及“钻石公主”号邮轮上撤离的美国公民中有21例确诊病例。
There were also 21 confirmed cases of American citizens evacuated from Wuhan, China, and the "Princess Diamond" cruise ship.
梅森尼尔表示，美国疾控中心仍在负责国内新冠病毒的大部分检测，正在解决检测试剂盒发往各州的问题。
Mason Neal says the CDC is still responsible for most of the testing of the new crown virus in the country and is addressing the issue of sending test kits to states.
美国公共卫生实验室协会（APHL）21日表示，目前美国只有三个州有能力对新冠病毒进行本地检测。
The American Association of Public Health Laboratories (APHL) said Thursday that only three states in the United States are currently able to conduct local testing of the new crown virus.
